A. General Information

 The Remuco project is hosted on SourceForge at http://remuco.sourceforge.net.
It is licensed under the GPLv2 or any newer version.

━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

